<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<%- include('./partials/head') %>
</head>

<body>
	<%- include('./partials/nav') %>
		<div class="container mt-5" id="mainBodyContainer">

			<div class="pinkify my-5">
				<article>
					<h3 class="text-center p-2">Some stats:</h3>
					<p class="text-center mt-3">Successful Requests: <%= requestsServed %></p>
					<p class="text-center mt-1">Catalogue Size: <%= itemCatalogueSize %></p>
				</article>
			</div>

			<div class="accordion pinkify" id="homeAccordian">
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<h2 class="accordion-header">
						<button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
							data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
							What is this?
						</button>
					</h2>
					<div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#homeAccordian">
						<div class="accordion-body">
							This is an implementation of christieBot's and tatatot234's minewind price guide as an API.
							This is not in any way affiliated with minecraft or minewind. Just something made by the
							player base for the player base.
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<h2 class="accordion-header">
						<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
							data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
							Why?
						</button>
					</h2>
					<div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#homeAccordian">
						<div class="accordion-body">
							You may or may not have noticed, but there are quite a few players on minewind that have
							created chat bots that are helpful to the general playerbase. Some players have tried making
							a price calculator, but the implementations are somewhat inconsistent (from a dev's POV,
							there is no dataset so it is hard).
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="accordion-item">
					<h2 class="accordion-header">
						<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
							data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
							Pricing System
						</button>
					</h2>
					<div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#homeAccordian">
						<div class="accordion-body">
							Completely identical to the essence sheets.
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>